Release history for perl-Perl-PrereqScanner-Scanner-Hint

v0.1.1 @ 2016-12-28 20:18 UTC

    -   Hints should start with two hashes now. `Perl::Critic` uses two hashes to start
        "magical annotations", let we support this tradition.

    -   **DEPRECATION** Hints started with one hash are recognized but deprecated and causes
        warning.

v0.1.0 @ 2015-10-22 11:14 UTC

    -   Initial release.
